sources.title: Ticks (1993) - Full Movie
sources.description:
A group of troubled teenagers is led by social workers on a California wilderness retreat, not knowing that the woods they are camping in have become infested by mutated, blood-sucking ticks. 

Starring Seth Green, Clint Howard and Alfonso Ribeiro.

#freemovies #moviesondemand #fullmovie

metadata.Plot: Problem teens in Los Angeles join an inner-city wilderness project in and attempt to get back in touch with life's priorities, led by do-gooders Holly and Charles. When they get to the campsite, they begin having problems adjusting to the wild life, particularly local marijuana growers using herbal steroids to accelerate plant growth, and the mutated ticks that the leaky steroid system has created.
metadata.Actors: Rosalind Allen, Ami Dolenz, Seth Green
